{
  "stem": "25773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Thebbnz were like that, T-H-E-B-B-N-Z, Shultz, S-L-U-- no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-H-U-L-T-Z.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shultz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow this were shops.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were German shops.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were German firms who were assigned-- they probably got permission from the German, from the Nazi government-- to stage the shops and a lot, a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And have the Jews laborers, slave laborers, to stitch uniforms for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[COUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got an announcement one day that we should move into the premises and leave our own flat in 26 [GERMAN] Street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father said us, to my stepmother and me, and all the other people who lived there, but predominantly us, to bring-- we still had, you know, like in every Jewish home, there was a lot of beautiful crockery from [?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Carlsbad, ?] from Marienbad, from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "God knows, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he succeeded to get the big ladder in the little kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kitchen was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to bring, my stepmother and I, from the cupboards wherever we kept, crammed these things, and to give it to him, each, you know, services of crockery, of beautiful you know, sets. 12, 12, 12.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from the top of the ladder, he slammed it down to the floor, so that it should be broken to pieces.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't want to leave it for the Germans, or for the Poles, or for anybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the minute we left this flat in [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fada ?] and were incarcerated in Schultz Thebbnz shops, we knew there would be no return.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So every single bit of this beautiful crockery was broken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Up, he was standing there, and [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- ?] and dropped to the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And every other thing, whatever we could damage, we damaged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a curious thing happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
